  "instructions": "This vocabulary list is dominated by verbs. As you read the base ~masu form, practice converting it to the ~te form in your head. (e.g. As you see 'Kaimasu', think 'Katte').",
  "contentItems": [
    {
      "type": "introduction",
      "text": "Remember: The syllable directly before 'masu' tells you the Group 1 rule. If it's a Group 2 verb (like Tabemasu or Mimasu), just drop masu."
    }
  ],
